  "body": "In Cinder cloud provider openstack https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/pkg/cloudprovider/providers/openstack/openstack_volumes.go#L234\r\nInside of AttachDisk function, it issues DetachDisk if it find out the the volume is currently attached to a different instance. This is very dangerous because it is very likely the volume is still mounted to that instance. The correct behavior should be fail this AttachDisk call. K8s attach_detach controller should handle unmount and detach volume safely.\r\n",
